1. INTRODUCTION
Thanks for visiting VANDALEAK.COM (“Website” or a “Service”) and / or downloading the VANDALEAK
APP (an “App Service”, and jointly with the Website, the “Services”) by Biokip Labs (hereafter, “Biokip”,
“us”, “we”, “our”). We built the App Service as a free and Ad Supported App with an in app purchase
option. The App Service is provided by Biokip at no cost and is intended for use as is.
Biokip is the controller and is responsible for your personal data. Our full contact details are as follows:
