6. THE INFORMATION WE COLLECT
We collect information in two main ways:
(I) you provide some data directly (such as by creating a user account), and
(II) we record some of it automatically
(I) Data you provide us:
– user name,
– country of residence,
– images of your work and
– if applicable, inquiries and emails to the Services or Biokip.
(II) Data we collect automatically:
– device associated user data,
– data we collect with cookies and similar technologies (please refer to below),
– data about your device, such as device name and operating system, browser type and language,
– general location data, and
– data about your use of the Service
